      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 72.1 - 老子 72.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 72.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>民不畏威，則大威至。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When the people do not fear what they ought to fear, that which is their great dread will come on them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-072__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-072</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 72.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 72.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>無狎其所居，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Let them not thoughtlessly indulge themselves in their ordinary life;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-072__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-072</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 72.4 - 老子 72.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 72.3 - 老子 72.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>無厭其所生。夫唯不厭，是以不厭。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>let them not act as if weary of what that life depends on. It is by avoiding such indulgence that such weariness does not arise.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
