      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 72.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故去彼取此。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>And thus he puts the latter alternative away and makes choice of the former.</seg>
      </tuv>
